{"tid":1559211,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【文宣組】入一入嚟！煮重中共米，同國際社會備案！","createTime":"2019-09-10T16:58:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T18:32:16.000Z","uid":259015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1ce78deaccc55b8ab34007a51ac48a89969bb9a2","tid":1559211,"uid":259015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"隔離好多post都講過，「焦土行動」計劃聽日無差別攻擊藍絲，唔理同路人定鬼，會唔會燒山無差別攻擊都好，<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔係割席</span></strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">但係一定要入晒中共數：</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登同Twitter 已有「分析」點解會係中共搞出嚟，自己睇，幫手推：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tomgrundy/status/1171121438377426944?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftomgrundy%2Fstatus%2F1171121438377426944%3Fs%3D21&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=0d2f4a9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftomgrundy%2Fstatus%2F1171121438377426944%3Fs%3D21&h=58db8054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tomgrundy/status/1171121438377426944?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nouvelleshk/status/1171274027060596736?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnouvelleshk%2Fstatus%2F1171274027060596736%3Fs%3D21&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=a9ce42dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnouvelleshk%2Fstatus%2F1171274027060596736%3Fs%3D21&h=d6bffb23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nouvelleshk/status/1171274027060596736?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n中共懷疑係香港策動911恐怖襲擊嘅證據<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1558494\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1558494</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住記住tag埋外國媒體，CNN呢啲唔少得！！<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，唔該大家喺各大平台寫一寫點解9.11香港「恐襲」會係中共策劃搞散場運動：<br />\n整體上就係咁：<br />\n1）香港人過去幾日先努力爭取美國支持，點會轉個頭喺美國國殤搞事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />難道示威者唔想美國幫手通過民主及人權法案？<br />\n<br />\n2）黨媒一早就開始大肆宣傳，好似驚人唔知咁，用美國911做background引起美國佬輿論。如果唔係佢哋計劃嘅，點會一早宣傳定？會等佢發生咗再大大力攻擊示威者啦，所以有可能係共產黨自編自導自演<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3）示威者一向係對準政權、警權，絕無作出任何無差別攻擊。相反，無差別攻擊一向係共產黨喺呢場運動嘅伎倆，7.21縱容元朗白衣人，8.31警察無差別攻擊市民，所以今次9.11無差別攻擊市民嘅謠言好可能係共產黨重施故技<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4）9月1日中共喉舌曾經話月圓之夜就係示威停止之時。月圓就係9月13中秋節，同所計畫嘅9月11恐襲不謀而合... 應該係中共自編自導自演一場恐襲，引發國際輿論反彈，孤立國際對香港嘅援助，繼而令到今次運動結束<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5）最唔想人權法案通過嘅係邊個？係中共！9月11吹風搞咁多野出嚟，目的就係挑撥港美關係，令到美國唔再幫香港通過法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">隨便揀一個，寫中英文放上Twitter！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣一定要做好，同國際社會備定案，順便講係中共策略！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f947579d849de440c9ecbb73366b6605666ed1","tid":1559211,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:03:59.000Z","msg":"文宣請幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請即參與：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>#wtsappforhk campaign (#eye4hk 2.0)</strong></span><br />\n有twitter既快啲retweet，無twitter既而家開番個<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>本地線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 將警暴，藍絲，官員，議員罪證狂推比警察<br />\n<br />\n2. 為左令每一個負責mon住既阿sir都不愁寂莫，每個人睇番自己生日日子既最後一位數字，揀下表有同樣最尾位數字既電話<br />\n<br />\n3. 有關如何保護自己，請搜尋「太空」等相關字眼<br />\n<br />\n5566 9500<br />\n5566 9501<br />\n5566 9502<br />\n5566 9503<br />\n5566 9504<br />\n5566 9505<br />\n5566 9506<br />\n5566 9507<br />\n5566 9508<br />\n5566 9509<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>國際線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. retweet手足既呢條tweet, 記住comment加#wtsappforhk<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeReoT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=5e64679a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhongkongers8%2Fstatus%2F1171379846447919104%3Fs%3D21&h=44f2ff93\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hongkongers8/status/1171379846447919104?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 如果你選擇將10個電話重新打一次出黎，記得加+852<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1. 成本低<br />\n2. 可以迫大家儲下唔同角度文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n壞處：<br />\n1. 本地線唔會要大家post番個舉報cap圖出黎，少左第二次marketing機會 (which is fine)<br />\n2. 外國人參與國際線程度成疑，但我覺得以campaign之名，行宣傳之實。就咁講#chinazi，#culturalrevolution，老實講有d悶。"},{"pid":"1e3d5bc67081f6f5b8ab1265a8160ae0116c408a","tid":1559211,"uid":259015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66f947579d849de440c9ecbb73366b6605666ed1","tid":1559211,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:03:59.000Z","msg":"文宣請幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請即參與：<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>#wtsappforhk campaign (#eye4hk 2.0)</strong></span><br />\n有twitter既